data.value: specifically the virus’ spike protein. Once injected into the body, the mRNA instructs the cells to produce antigens - such as the spike protein mentioned – which are then detected by immune cells, triggering a response by the body’s lymphocytes. Whoever is exposed to the COVID-19 coronavirus in the future would have an immune system that recognises it, and in turn fight off the infection.

data.name: bunifuLabel4.Text
data.value: The idea of this app is to illustrate and disseminate properly to the customers, data that are important and relevant in this time of pandemic. Notably, data about vaccines, its efficacy, availability, and the number of people vaccinated in the Philippines. The developers will be using illustrations, graphs, charts, and data visualization tools to help the user comprehend the numbers that are being presented on the screen. This combined with a fresh and sleek UI to give the user a premium experience while having the convenience of information at all the same place.
